    "uid": "John_Briley_1",
    "intro": "John Richard Briley (June 25, 1925 - December 14, 2019) was an American writer best known for screenplays of biographical films. He won the Best Original Screenplay at the 55th Academy Awards for Gandhi (1982). As well as film scripts, he wrote for television and theatre, and published several novels."
